duties_responsibilities.duty: Loading, unloading, sorting, picking, stocking, staging, fabrication, and transportation of goods.
Install protective devices and verify computations against the physical count of stock.
Receive and fulfill orders, sell supplies, materials, and products to installers and subcontractors.
Drive truck to pick up incoming stock, deliver materials, operate forklift or other machinery.

education_certification.credential: HS Diploma or GED strongly preferred. 0-2 years of experience in area of responsibility.
